entries.femaleVariant: Oh... a friendly face.
Didn't work out with Jason?
Didn't pan out with Jason, huh?
Totally not my type. I'll make sure Dakota knows to only send me you from now on.
Might not have the occasion. You oughta keep a low profile for a while.
Know what I missed most in that basement?
Booze? Cigs?
Barely let you out of my sight.
Melons. Those sweet, honey melons Dakota's folks got growin' on genetic mishmash.
Miles above any syn-melons you could find.
OK...
I sat there thinking... what I wouldn't give for one taste of that sweet, sweet melon.
'Course that prick Jason wouldn't entertain the thought.
Heh. You're great to work with.
Let you outta my sight for one minute...
I know, I know... Now you play postman and deliver me to Dakota.
All right, let's get you outta here.
But maybe I'll have the honor to return the favor someday.
Sure, maybe.
Ugh... shit. Feel like I haven't used my legs for a straight month.
Oh, a new face.
See Militech's been investing in young talent.
So... you here to take me on a little field trip?
Dakota sent me.
Why'd Militech want to buy you?
I'm here on Dakota's behalf.
For chrissakes – now you're telling me?!
I loathe it, this whole "playing tough in the face of death" thing.
Why'd Militech want to buy you off of Jason?
What – you miss the memo?
That NCC crook, McLean. Militech bought him off – drafted bills he passed without a blink.
I took the bastard out, but now they're desperate to find a fall-guy. Don't want the NCPD looking too close into the matter.
As upstanding citizens would do.
Mhm. Militech's gladly gonna pin me for a heap other things, since I'm already here.
I can only surmise I'll be so desperate as to end up "taking my own life," as they say...
Sorry to hear that.
Let's get out of here.
Handled yourself well.
Handled yourself well.
Should've seen how that fool Jason gobbled it up.
Even started holstering in the small-of-the-back like me.
